Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • birdgame.Model
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Model contains and deals with the basic logic of the game, including updating an object's location and direction, handling collisions, spawning obstacles, and player progress.
